com.locuslabs.sdk.maps.model

Class Marker.Symbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.locuslabs.sdk.maps.model.Marker.Symbol
  • Enclosing interface:
    Marker

    public static class Marker.Symbol
extends Object
    Symbol Required: path - the symbol's path, a custom path expressed in SVG path notation. Optional: anchor - the position of the symbol relative to the marker. default: (0, 0) fillColor - the symbol's SVG fill color. all SVG colors are are supported. default: 'black'. fillOpacity - the symbol's SVG fill opacity. default: 0 rotation - the angle by which to rotate the original symbol, clockwise in degrees. default: 0 scale - the factor by which to scale the symbol in size. default: 1 strokeColor - the symbol's SVG stroke color. all SVG colors are supported. default: 'black'. strokeOpacity - the symbol's SVG stroke opacity. default: 1 strokeWeight - the symbol's SVG stroke weight. default: 1
